ce\n|Pilot\n|-\n|2011\n|''[[Mildred Pierce (miniseries)|Mildred Pierce]]''\n|Mrs. Forrester\n|3 episodes\n|-\n|2012\u20132013\n|''[[The Newsroom (U.S. TV series)|The Newsroom]]''\n|Nina Howard\n|5 episodes\n|-\n|2013\n|''[[Law & Order: Special Victims Unit]]''\n|Viola Mesner\n|Episode: \"Born Psychopath\"\n|-\n|2013\n|''The Ordained''\n|Packy\n|Pilot\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Allegiance (TV series)|Allegiance]]''\n|Katya O'Connor\n|13 episodes\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Last Week Tonight with John Oliver]]''\n|Herself\n|Episode: \"Infrastructures\"\n|-\n|2015\u20132016\n|''[[Wayward Pines]]''\n|Megan Fisher\n|14 episodes\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[American Crime (TV series)|American Crime]]''\n|Steph Sullivan\n|7 episodes\n|-\n|2018\u20132019\n|''[[For the People (2018 TV series)|For the People]]''\n|Jill Carlan\n|20 episodes\n|-\n|2018\u20132019\n|''[[Strange Angel]]''\n|Ruth Parsons\n|7 episodes\n|-\n|-\n|2020\n|''[[Nova (American TV program)|Nova]]''\n|Narrator\n|1 epsode\n|-\n|TBA\n|''[[Your Honor (miniseries)|Your Honor]]''\n|Gina\n|Upcoming miniseries\n|}\n\n==Stage==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n|1992\n|''[[Goodnight Desdemona (Good Morning Juliet)]]''\n| Juliett / Student / Soldier of Cyprus\n|[[ East 13th Street Theater| East 13th Street Theatre]]\n|-\n|1992\n|''Two Shakespearean Actors''\n|Miss Anne Holland\n|[[Cort Theatre]]\n|-\n|1993\n|''[[Measure for Measure]]''\n|Mariana\n|[[Delacorte Theater]]\n|-\n|1993\n|''Pterodactyls''\n|Emma Duncan\n|[[Vineyard Theatre]]\n|-\n|1995\u20131996\n|''The Food Chain''\n|Amanda\n|[[Westside Theatre]]\n|-\n|1997\u20131998\n|''[[Ivanov (play)|Ivanov]]''\n|Sasha\n|[[Vivian Beaumont Theatre]]\n|-\n|2000\n|''[[Spinning Into Butter]]''\n|Sarah\n|[[Lincoln Center]]\n|-\n|2005\n|''Hope Leaves the Theater''\n|Various roles\n|[[St. Ann's Warehouse]]\n|-\n|2009\n|''[[God of Carnage]]''\n|Annette \n|[[Bernard B. Jacobs Theatre]]\n|-\n|2016\u20132017\n|''The Red Barn''\n|Ingrid Dodd\n|[[Roya